<subSubSection pageId="31" pageNumber="32" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="31.[151,1437,1600,1771]" pageId="31" pageNumber="32">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,322,1672,1698]" pageId="31" pageNumber="32">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
Pronotum with protuberances; lateral tubercles of the prothorax placed medially or on posterior third; elytra with setose granules, sometimes throughout.
</paragraph>
